set s=ES[GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetDyingUnit()))]+GetPlayerName(GetOwningPlayer(GetDyingUnit()))+"|r's Ancient of War has been pwned by "+ES[GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetKillingUnit()))]+GetPlayerName(GetOwningPlayer(GetKillingUnit()))+"|r for 20 gold!"
set s2=ES[GetPlayerId(p)]+GetPlayerName(p)+" has been defeated.|r"
